<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-lg cursor-pointer font-headline-lg text-headline-lg font-bold" style="list-style:none;"><span>What file formats are supported?</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" style="font-size:20px;">expand_more</span></summary>
<div class="px-lg pb-lg font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed" style="border-top:1px solid var(--card-border);padding-top:16px;">We support JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, SVG, PDF, and Figma share links. Maximum file size is 50 MB for standard uploads.</div>
</details>
<details class="glass-card rounded-xl group" style="padding:0;">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-lg cursor-pointer font-headline-lg text-headline-lg font-bold" style="list-style:none;"><span>How accurate is the font detection?</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" style="font-size:20px;">expand_more</span></summary>
<div class="px-lg pb-lg font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed" style="border-top:1px solid var(--card-border);padding-top:16px;">Our font detection achieves 99.8% accuracy on clean images and 94% on complex backgrounds. The system matches against 100+ font families and provides confidence scores for every detection.</div>
</details>
<details class="glass-card rounded-xl group" style="padding:0;">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-lg cursor-pointer font-headline-lg text-headline-lg font-bold" style="list-style:none;"><span>Is my design data private?</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" style="font-size:20px;">expand_more</span></summary>
<div class="px-lg pb-lg font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed" style="border-top:1px solid var(--card-border);padding-top:16px;">Absolutely. Uploaded designs are processed in memory and never stored on our servers longer than necessary. We do not use your designs for training or share them with third parties.</div>
</details>
<details class="glass-card rounded-xl group" style="padding:0;">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-lg cursor-pointer font-headline-lg text-headline-lg font-bold" style="list-style:none;"><span>Can I use it commercially?</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" style="font-size:20px;">expand_more</span></summary>
<div class="px-lg pb-lg font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed" style="border-top:1px solid var(--card-border);padding-top:16px;">Yes. Pro and Team plans include commercial usage rights. The Free plan is limited to personal and educational use with up to 5 analyses per month.</div>
</details>
<details class="glass-card rounded-xl group" style="padding:0;">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-lg cursor-pointer font-headline-lg text-headline-lg font-bold" style="list-style:none;"><span>Do I need an account to try it?</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" style="font-size:20px;">expand_more</span></summary>
<div class="px-lg pb-lg font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed" style="border-top:1px solid var(--card-border);padding-top:16px;">You can explore the platform and view demo analyses without an account. To upload your own designs and save results, you will need to create a free account.</div>
</details>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section class="py-xl px-md" style="background:var(--surface-container-low);">
